<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Relay Overlay</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="styles/design-system.css">

    <style>
        body,
        html {
            height: 100%;
            width: 100%;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            overflow: hidden;
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            justify-content: flex-end;
        }

        /* === OVERLAY LAYER SYSTEM === */
        #layer-0-status {
            position: fixed;
            top: 0;
            left: 0;
            right: 0;
            z-index: 100;
            pointer-events: none;
        }

        #layer-1-alerts {
            position: fixed;
            top: 0;
            right: 0;
            z-index: 200;
            pointer-events: none;
        }

        #layer-2-captions {
            position: fixed;
            bottom: 0;
            left: 0;
            right: 0;
            z-index: 300;
            display: flex;
            justify-content: center;
            padding: 20px;
        }

        #layer-3-guidance {
            position: fixed;
            top: 0;
            left: 0;
            right: 0;
            bottom: 0;
            z-index: 400;
            pointer-events: none;
        }

        #layer-3-guidance > * {
            pointer-events: auto;
        }

        #layer-4-emergency {
            position: fixed;
            top: 0;
            left: 0;
            right: 0;
            bottom: 0;
            z-index: 500;
            pointer-events: none;
            display: none;
        }

        /* === ALERT OVERLAY (legacy flash) === */
        #alert-overlay {
            position: absolute;
            top: 0;
            left: 0;
            width: 100%;
            height: 100%;
            z-index: 10;
            pointer-events: none;
            opacity: 0;
            transition: opacity 0.2s;
        }

        #alert-overlay.active {
            opacity: 1;
        }

        #alert-overlay.danger {
            background: rgba(255, 59, 48, 0.3);
            box-shadow: inset 0 0 100px var(--color-emergency);
        }

        #alert-overlay.warning {
            background: rgba(255, 204, 0, 0.3);
            box-shadow: inset 0 0 100px var(--color-warning);
        }

        /* === CAPTION BAR === */
        #caption-bar {
            width: 100%;
            max-width: 900px;
            min-height: 80px;
            max-height: 180px;
            padding: 16px 24px;
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            pointer-events: auto;

            opacity: 0;
            transform: translateY(20px);
            animation: slideUpFade 0.6s var(--transition-smooth) forwards;
        }

        .caption-toolbar {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-between;
            align-items: center;
            flex-shrink: 0;
            padding-bottom: 8px;
            border-bottom: 1px solid var(--color-border);
            margin-bottom: 8px;
        }

        .caption-content {
            flex: 1;
            overflow: hidden;
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            gap: 8px;
        }

        @keyframes slideUpFade {
            to {
                opacity: 1;
                transform: translateY(0);
            }
        }

        @keyframes spin {
            to { transform: rotate(360deg); }
        }

        @keyframes alertPulse {
            0%, 100% { box-shadow: 0 4px 20px rgba(255,59,48,0.3); }
            50% { box-shadow: 0 4px 30px rgba(255,59,48,0.6); }
        }

        .conversation-text {
            font-size: var(--font-size-xl);
            font-weight: 500;
            line-height: 1.3;
            text-align: left;
            transition: color 0.3s;
            overflow-y: auto;
            max-height: 100px;
        }

        .conversation-text .caption-segment {
            margin-bottom: 4px;
        }

        .conversation-text .caption-word {
            transition: opacity 0.15s;
        }

        .status-indicator {
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 6px;
            font-size: var(--font-size-xs);
            color: var(--color-secondary);
            font-weight: 500;
            letter-spacing: 0.5px;
            text-transform: uppercase;
        }

        /* === MEETING MODE BADGE === */
        #meeting-badge {
            display: none;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 6px;
            background: rgba(255, 59, 48, 0.15);
            border: 1px solid rgba(255, 59, 48, 0.3);
            padding: 4px 10px;
            border-radius: 20px;
            font-size: 11px;
            color: #ff6b6b;
            margin-left: 10px;
        }

        .drag-handle {
            width: 60px;
            height: 5px;
            background: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.2);
            border-radius: 3px;
            margin: 8px auto 0 auto;
            cursor: grab;
            -webkit-app-region: drag;
            transition: all 0.2s;
            flex-shrink: 0;
        }

        .drag-handle:hover {
            background: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.4);
            width: 80px;
        }

        .drag-handle:active {
            cursor: grabbing;
        }

        .dot {
            width: 8px;
            height: 8px;
            border-radius: 50%;
            background-color: var(--color-secondary);
            transition: background-color 0.3s;
        }

        .dot.active {
            background-color: var(--color-success);
            box-shadow: 0 0 8px var(--color-success);
        }

        .dot.listening {
            animation: pulse 1.5s infinite;
        }

        @keyframes pulse {
            0% { transform: scale(1); opacity: 1; }
            50% { transform: scale(1.4); opacity: 0.6; }
            100% { transform: scale(1); opacity: 1; }
        }

        .tool-btn {
            width: 24px;
            height: 24px;
            border-radius: 50%;
            background: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
            color: var(--color-text);
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            cursor: pointer;
            transition: all 0.2s;
            font-size: 14px;
            pointer-events: auto;
            -webkit-app-region: no-drag;
            margin-left: 8px;
        }

        .tool-btn:hover {
            background: var(--color-background-dark);
            color: var(--color-text-dark);
        }

        #tts-container {
            display: none;
            flex-direction: row;
            width: 100%;
            margin-top: 8px;
            pointer-events: auto;
            -webkit-app-region: no-drag;
        }

        #tts-container.active {
            display: flex;
        }

        #tts-input {
            flex: 1;
            padding: 8px 12px;
            border-radius: var(--radius-md);
            border: 1px solid var(--color-border);
            font-size: 16px;
            outline: none;
            background: var(--color-surface);
            color: var(--color-text);
        }

        #video-container {
            position: relative;
            width: 160px;
            height: 120px;
            border-radius: 12px;
            overflow: hidden;
            border: 2px solid var(--color-accent);
            background: black;
            display: none;
            margin-top: 8px;
        }

        #video-container.active {
            display: block;
        }

        #input_video {
            width: 100%;
            height: 100%;
            object-fit: cover;
            transform: scaleX(-1);
        }

        .close-btn {
            width: 24px;
            height: 24px;
            border-radius: 50%;
            background: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
            color: var(--color-text);
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            cursor: pointer;
            transition: all 0.2s;
            font-size: 14px;
            pointer-events: auto;
            -webkit-app-region: no-drag;
        }

        .close-btn:hover {
            background: var(--color-emergency);
            color: white;
        }

        #visualizer {
            width: 60px;
            height: 30px;
            margin-right: 12px;
        }

        /* === CONFUSION HELP INDICATOR === */
        #confusion-help {
            position: fixed;
            bottom: 210px;
            left: 20px;
            background: rgba(29, 29, 31, 0.92);
            backdrop-filter: blur(20px);
            -webkit-backdrop-filter: blur(20px);
            border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.1);
            border-radius: 12px;
            padding: 10px 14px;
            color: #f5f5f7;
            font-size: 13px;
            display: none;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 8px;
            cursor: pointer;
            pointer-events: auto;
            transition: all 0.3s ease;
            z-index: 300;
            max-width: 280px;
        }

        #confusion-help:hover {
            background: rgba(0, 113, 227, 0.3);
        }
    </style>
</head>

<body>
    <div id="alert-overlay"></div>

    <!-- Layer 0: Status -->
    <div id="layer-0-status"></div>

    <!-- Layer 1: Sound Alerts -->
    <div id="layer-1-alerts" id="alert-container"></div>

    <!-- Layer 2: Captions -->
    <div id="layer-2-captions">
        <div id="caption-bar" class="glass-panel">
            <!-- Fixed Toolbar -->
            <div class="caption-toolbar">
                <div style="display:flex;align-items:center;">
                    <div class="status-indicator">
                        <div class="dot active listening"></div>
                        <span id="status-text">Listening...</span>
                    </div>
                    <div id="meeting-badge"></div>
                </div>
                <div style="display: flex; align-items: center;">
                    <canvas id="visualizer"></canvas>
                    <div id="transcript-btn" class="tool-btn" title="Transcript History">📜</div>
                    <div id="nav-toggle" class="tool-btn" title="Ask AI Guide (Cmd+Shift+H)">🧭</div>
                    <div id="tts-toggle" class="tool-btn" title="Type to Speak">⌨️</div>
                    <div id="minimize-btn" class="tool-btn" title="Minimize">−</div>
                    <div id="close-btn" class="tool-btn" title="Close">✕</div>
                </div>
            </div>

            <!-- Scrollable Content -->
            <div class="caption-content">
                <div id="video-container">
                    <video id="input_video"></video>
                </div>
                <div id="transcript" class="conversation-text">
                    Waiting for speech...
                </div>

                <div id="tts-container">
                    <input type="text" id="tts-input" placeholder="Type to speak...">
                    <select id="tts-output-select" title="Select Audio Output">
                        <option value="default">Default Output</option>
                    </select>
                    <div id="audio-help-btn" class="tool-btn"
                        style="width: 20px; height: 20px; font-size: 12px; margin-left: 5px;">?</div>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="drag-handle" title="Drag to move"></div>
        </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Layer 3: Guidance (AI panels, command bar, screen explainer) -->
    <div id="layer-3-guidance"></div>

    <!-- Layer 4: Emergency (blocking modal) -->
    <div id="layer-4-emergency"></div>

    <!-- Confusion Help Indicator -->
    <div id="confusion-help">
        <span>💡</span>
        <span id="confusion-msg">Need help?</span>
    </div>

    <!-- Audio Connection Guide Modal -->
    <div id="audio-guide-modal"
        style="display: none; position: fixed; top: 0; left: 0; width: 100%; height: 100%; background: rgba(0,0,0,0.8); z-index: 1000; align-items: center; justify-content: center; backdrop-filter: blur(5px);">
        <div
            style="background: var(--color-surface); padding: 30px; border-radius: 16px; width: 400px; color: var(--color-text); border: 1px solid var(--color-border); box-shadow: 0 10px 30px rgba(0,0,0,0.5);">
            <h2 style="margin-top: 0;">🎧 Connect to Zoom/FaceTime</h2>
            <p>To let others hear the AI voice in calls, you need a <b>Virtual Audio Cable</b>.</p>
            <ol style="padding-left: 20px; line-height: 1.6;">
                <li>Install <b>BlackHole 2ch</b> or <b>VB-Cable</b> (Free).</li>
                <li>In Relay (here), select the Cable as <b>Audio Output</b>.</li>
                <li>In Zoom/Teams, select the Cable as your <b>Microphone</b>.</li>
            </ol>
            <button id="close-guide-btn"
                style="background: var(--color-accent); color: white; border: none; padding: 10px 20px; border-radius: 8px; cursor: pointer; float: right; font-weight: 600;">Got
                it</button>
        </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Meeting Summary Modal -->
    <div id="meeting-summary-modal"
        style="display: none; position: fixed; top: 0; left: 0; width: 100%; height: 100%; background: rgba(0,0,0,0.8); z-index: 1000; align-items: center; justify-content: center; backdrop-filter: blur(5px);">
        <div style="background: var(--color-surface); padding: 30px; border-radius: 16px; width: 600px; max-height: 80vh; overflow-y: auto; color: var(--color-text); border: 1px solid var(--color-border); box-shadow: 0 10px 30px rgba(0,0,0,0.5);">
            <div style="display:flex;justify-content:space-between;align-items:center;margin-bottom:16px;">
                <h2 style="margin:0;">📝 Meeting Summary</h2>
                <button id="close-summary-btn" style="background:rgba(255,255,255,0.1);border:none;color:var(--color-text);width:30px;height:30px;border-radius:50%;cursor:pointer;font-size:16px;">✕</button>
            </div>
            <div id="meeting-summary-content" style="line-height:1.6;white-space:pre-wrap;"></div>
            <div style="margin-top:16px;display:flex;gap:8px;justify-content:flex-end;">
                <button id="export-summary-btn" style="background:var(--color-accent);color:white;border:none;padding:8px 16px;border-radius:8px;cursor:pointer;font-weight:500;">Export</button>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>

    <script type="module" src="app.js"></script>
</body>

</html>
